When asked if he'd played as well before, Hart said: 'Not really. It's just unfortunate after the first leg.

'It's nice to save a penalty off Messi but I wanted it to count. Unfortunately, it hasn't. I'm here to make saves. A lot hit me tonight, I tried to be big.

'It was busy. Definitely busy. I tried to smother them best I could. I know full well they've got a pass at all times. That's why I tried to rush them.

