‘My job was to try and rush them. Against quality players that's difficult to do sometimes. You need a bit of luck.'

‘We look to West Brom now. Big shout to the fans who came here up in the clouds. We're going to turn up Saturday, and go again.’

Hart’s performance grabbed the attentions of the pundits, too, as the former Shrewsbury Town youngster spared his teammate’s blushes with his non-stop blocks and saves.

